"72:10:13" : {s: 72, a: 10, w: 13, r: "رشد", t: "رَشَدًۭا", l: "رَشَد", lc: 5, tl: "rashadan", lb: "সততা, ন্যায়পরায়নতা, হেদায়েত, ",e: "a right path", b: "সঠিক কাজ", f: 5, rm: "to follow the right way, be well guided or directed, true direction, correct rule of action, straight forwardness, maturity of a child/intellect, capacity to manage ones affairs."},
