"72:13:9" : {s: 72, a: 13, w: 9, r: "ربب", t: "بِرَبِّهِۦ", l: "رَبّ", lc: 975, tl: "birabbihi", lb: "প্রভু, সযত্নে পালনকর্তা ",e: "in his Lord", b: "তারা প্রভুর প্রতি", f: 1, rm: "to be a lord and master, collect, possess/owner, rule, increase, complete, bring up, preserve, chief, guardian, regulator, determiner, caretaker, provider, sustainer, perfecter, rewarder, creator, maintainer, reposer of properties, developer, former of rules and laws of the growth, foster a thing in such a manner as to make it attain one condition after another until it reaches its goal of completion, the bringing a thing to a state of completion by degrees, whoever possesses a thing is its rabb."},
