"72:13:14" : {s: 72, a: 13, w: 14, r: "رهق", t: "رَهَقًۭا", l: "رَهَق", lc: 2, tl: "rahaqan", lb: "অবাধ্যতা, অহঙ্কার, বাড়াবাড়ি",e: "any burden", b: "অন্যায়, আত্মম্ভরী", f: 2, rm: "to follow closely, cover, be foolish, lie, be mischievous, be ungodly, hasten, overtake, reach, draw near, overspread. rahaqa - to oppress, cause to suffer, be given to evil practices. rahqun - folly, oppression, evil disposition. arhaqa - to impose a difficult task, afflict with troubles and difficulties."},
